name: Rune NFT #101
description: A Rune sacred to Tyr, Lord of the Heavens and war leader. Right Side: A rune of bravery and steadfastness in the face of any adversity. New partnerships will produce great things. This is a rune of energy, contentment and passion and it is a much-used talisman. Other meanings include: a brave and noble death, self-knowledge, faith, victory and success in law and war. Reversed: This rune reversed is symbolic of frustrations and quarrels that sap the strength.
